ed college.<\/p>\n<div><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/college-instagram-statistic1.png\" alt=\"College Instagram\" width=\"750\" height=\"479\" \/><\/div>\n<p>7. 26% of Instagram users make more than <a href=\"http:\/\/louisem.com\/152018\/instagram-stats-2017\">$75,000 per year<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h2>Instagram Usage Statistics<\/h2>\n<p>1. The most followed account as of 2021 belongs to\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/cristiano\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Cristiano Ronaldo<\/a>\u00a0has 315.75\u00a0million and is followed by\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/therock\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Dwayne\u00a0Johnson<\/a>\u00a0at 275 million.<br \/>\n2. The record for the most-liked\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.statista.com\/statistics\/673810\/instagram-posts-most-likes\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Instagram<\/a>\u00a0post belongs to a satirical account,<a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/world_record_egg\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\u00a0@world_record_egg<\/a>, made to surpass popular celebrities&#8217; posts\u2014which garnered almost 56 million likes.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-45839 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/2022-instagram-statistics-most-liked-post.jpg\" alt=\"2022-instagram-statistics-most-liked-post\" width=\"720\" height=\"412\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/2022-instagram-statistics-most-liked-post.jpg 720w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/2022-instagram-statistics-most-liked-post-480x275.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 720px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<div><\/div>\n<p>3. As of 2021, there are\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/social-media-statistics\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">over 1 billion active Instagrammers.<\/a><br \/>\n4. <a href=\"https:\/\/instagram-press.com\/our-story\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Half of those users<\/a> (500 million) are active every day<strong>.<\/strong><br \/>\n5. There are <a href=\"https:\/\/trends.google.com\/trends\/\">16,600,000 Google searches<\/a> for &#8220;instagram&#8221; per month.<br \/>\n6. There are <a href=\"https:\/\/trends.google.com\/trends\/\">165,000 searches<\/a> per month for &#8220;kylie jenner instagram&#8221;<br \/>\n7. 51% of Instagram users <a href=\"http:\/\/www.pewinternet.org\/2016\/11\/11\/social-media-update-2016-methodology\/\">access the platform daily<\/a>, and 35% say they look at the platform several times per day.<br \/>\n8. 95 million photos and videos are shared on Instagram <a href=\"https:\/\/business.instagram.com\/blog\/500000-advertisers\/\">per day<\/a>.<br \/>\n9. Over <a href=\"https:\/\/business.instagram.com\/blog\/500000-advertisers\/\">40 billion photos<\/a> and videos have been shared on the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2018\/06\/13\/instagram-algorithm\">Instagram platform<\/a> since its conception.<\/p>\n<p><strong>RELATED:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2022\/01\/11\/most-popular-social-media-platforms\">The 6 Biggest, Baddest Social Media Platforms (and How to Wield Their Power).<\/a> Put your armor on.<\/p>\n<h2>Instagram Business Statistics<\/h2>\n<p>1.\u00a0There are over\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.omnicoreagency.com\/instagram-statistics\/#:~:text=There%20are%20more%20than%20200,follow%20at%20least%20one%20brand.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">200\u00a0million business profiles<\/a>\u00a0using Instagram worldwide in 2021.<br \/>\n2.\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/webdam.com\/blog\/brand-marketing-infographic\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">60% of the top brands\u00a0<\/a>on Instagram use the same filter for every post.<br \/>\n3. Over 80% of accounts on Instagram follow a business, and over <a href=\"https:\/\/business.instagram.com\/blog\/25-million-businesses\/\">200 million Instagrammers<\/a> actively a business profile every day.<\/p>\n<div><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/instagram-ad-statistic.jpg\" alt=\"Instagram Advertising Statistics\" width=\"500\" height=\"772\" \/><\/div>\n<p>4. It\u2019s estimated that Instagram brought in\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.businessofapps.com\/data\/instagram-statistics\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">$24\u00a0billion<\/a>\u00a0in revenue in 2020, accounting for roughly 36.9% of Facebook\u2019s annual revenue.<br \/>\n5.\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/social-media-statistics\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">More than 80%<\/a>\u00a0of businesses say engagement is the most important metric to measure for Instagram marketing.<br \/>\n6. Currently in 2021, over\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/social-media-statistics\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">70% of U.S. companies<\/a>\u00a0use Instagram for\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2019\/04\/09\/ecommerce-brands\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">marketing<\/a>.<br \/>\n7.\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/social-media-statistics\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">9<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/social-media-statistics\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">0% of Instagram users<\/a>\u00a0follow at least one business on the platform.<br \/>\n8.\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/social-media-statistics\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">81%<\/a>\u00a0of people use Instagram to research products or services.<\/p>\n<h2>Instagram Content Statistics<\/h2>\n<p>1. <a href=\"https:\/\/techcrunch.com\/2017\/11\/01\/instagram-whatsapp-vs-snapchat\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">500 million users<\/a> use the \u201cstories\u201d feature daily<strong>.<\/strong><br \/>\n2. Instagram <a href=\"http: